channel.description:
This is bluurr's client base edited Credits 20% bluurr's 33 20% client tuts thank you guyz 33 50% me putting it together and fixing glitches 10% repentent drop the tgd
Base: Credits Delta 70% Tuts 20% Me 10% didnt do much just few edits
Added real barrows Move the custom items in there correct item place Move areas around like shops etc Fix donator icons Fix a few npc and skill glitches Made a more stable economy through npc drops Didn't get to add my pvp idea was in the process of that to use the old pk points system that when u kill someone u might get a rare out of it use to be done with party hats on old servers was going to switch it to drop to drop the new pvp items from custom client if anyone want to use that idea be my guess
Features of Client: New Jframe New Gframe Added new Cursors Added new background Added new configurations Added new update models d claws, d plate etc Added more new god wars npcs Added clan chat interface Added new theme switches Added a new x log button
Compatible with delta base server
Couldn't have done it without the Client tutorials
[img]http://i40.tinypic.com/262krye.jpg[/img] [img]http://i43.tinypic.com/33uu58z.jpg[/img] [img]http://i44.tinypic.com/dw3vgg.jpg[/img] [img]http://i39.tinypic.com/23ssl5j.jpg[/img]
Post if you download/what you think of it so i know what you think and tweak to your suggestions so i can make a better one maybe a v2 Client Download: http://files.filefront.com/Thee+Undergroundrar/;12603173;/fileinfo.html Source Download: http://files.filefront.com/Thee+Undergroundrar/;12603733;/fileinfo.html Btw the run is "CONSTRUCT" on my Client if you didnt know you can rename it back to run if you want [size=40pt] Ive Only Posted On Moparscape No where Else And On [u]Rune server[/u] My name is [u]Kidsub[/u][/size]
If You Leach Well Your A No Lifer
[size=24pt]GoodLuck I Hope My Source Is Good Enough The Reason I never Added Virus Scan Is because it says virus scans are usless and lus im not a nolifer..i like to code and like to get better[/size]
[size=22pt][b]Mini Tutorials[/b][/size] Source tut To Change Source Name Go Client.java And Hold ctrl and f and type Thee underground and edit it to what you want to call it, to change owners name search youbleedred and change it..
To edit bank go to texthandler and search project x and change it to what you wana call bank.
Client Tutorial:
changing loading name:Open Client.java and search thee underground and edit it to what you want to call it..
Changing ip address open Gui and search serverip and put in ur ip inside the " "
To change title of client search thee underground and edit it to what you want to call it.
But remember thease are basic tutorials
And 1 More thing Donator icon is added
to give donator type ::add , the person u gave donator cant see it but other players can.
If You also dont change other stuff apart from renaming and shit im goner kill you!!
